PrecisRe-appointment of KARIN REBECCA MICHNICK, of Montreal, Quebec, as a part-time member of the Convention Refugee Determination Division of the Immigration and Refugee Board (Montreal Regional Office), to hold office during good behaviour for a term of three years and six months, effective September 29, 1998.
